rows.label: tlk10030101_msg0002
rows.name:
Did you think I was dead?
Even I thought I was dead.

rows.label: tlk10030101_msg0003
rows.name:
Benkei told me not to die. She said
she wanted to be the one to kill me.

rows.label: tlk10030101_msg0004
rows.name:
I couldn't just let myself die after an
order like that. Honestly, I'd be scared
of the consequences.

rows.label: tlk10030101_msg0005
rows.name:
Well, you'll have to let me come along
to take a look at the answer that you
found.
